videos.headline: Fitzsimmons: Wideman's actions were 'nasty, disgusting'
videos.description: Ian Fitzsimmons and Mike Golic Jr. react to Flames veteran defenseman Dennis Wideman cross checking a linesman during the team's 2-1 home loss to the Predators.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NHL Analysis (Fitzsimmons: Wideman’s actions were ‘nasty, disgusting’) 2016/01/28 M&M PVC
